'''球員錦標賽'''（The Players Championship）是一個[[高爾夫球|高爾夫球]]比賽，也是[[PGA巡迴賽|PGA巡迴賽]]賽事之一，開始於1974年<ref name=hcmsanr>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=7UcxAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DUQDAAAAIBAJ&pg=2052%2C2968287 |newspaper=Rome News-Tribune |location=Georgia |title=Move over 'big four,' here comes another |last=Biggers |first=Don |date=June 23, 1974 |page=1C |accessdate=2021-05-09 |archive-date=2016-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160511160030/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=7UcxAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DUQDAAAAIBAJ&pg=2052,2968287 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。球員錦標賽的獎金額是所有高爾夫巡迴賽中最高的（自2020年起是1,500萬美元）。有時球員錦標賽也會被稱為「[[四大賽|第五大滿貫]]」，但這並未得到官方認可。和其他三個在美國舉行的高爾夫大滿貫賽事不同的是，球員錦標賽並不是歐巡賽的正式賽事。1982年開始，球員錦標賽固定在[[索格拉斯巡迴賽球手俱樂部|索格拉斯巡迴賽球手俱樂部]]舉辦<ref name=nyt-fifthmajor>{{cite news |title=Men’s Fifth Major May Remain Mythical |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/05/08/sports/golf/unlike-lpga-mens-tour-may-never-have-official-fifth-major.html?_r=0 |newspaper=The New York Times |first=Karen |last=Crouse |date=May 7, 2013 |access-date=June 27, 2013 |archive-date=2021-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512152349/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/05/08/sports/golf/unlike-lpga-mens-tour-may-never-have-official-fifth-major.html?_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=forbes-playersfifth>{{cite web |title=The Players Championship Is Not The "5th Major," But It's Still A Great Tournament |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/monteburke/2012/05/09/the-players-championship-is-not-the-5th-major-but-its-still-a-great-tournament/ |work=Forbes |first=Monte |last=Burke |date=May 9, 2012 |access-date=June 27, 2013 |archive-date=2021-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512184752/https://www.forbes.com/sites/monteburke/2012/05/09/the-players-championship-is-not-the-5th-major-but-its-still-a-great-tournament/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[男子高爾夫世界排名|世界排名前50位的高爾夫球手]]都可參加球員錦標賽。在2007年至2018年，球員錦標賽的第四輪比賽日是五月的第二個星期日（母親節），與之相對的是美國公開賽的第四輪比賽日則是六月的第三個星期日（父親節）。但從2019年開始，由於[[PGA錦標賽|PGA錦標賽]]的舉辦時間從8月改至5月，球員錦標賽改在每年3月舉行<ref>{{Cite magazine |url=https://www.golfdigest.com/story/the-pga-championship-is-moving-to-may-and-players-are-on-board |title=The PGA Championship is moving to May and players are on board |last=Shedloski |first=Dave |date=August 7, 2017 |magazine=Golf Digest |access-date=August 8, 2017 |archive-date=2021-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210518145326/https://www.golfdigest.com/story/the-pga-championship-is-moving-to-may-and-players-are-on-board |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/08/08/sports/golf/pga-championship-may.html |title=P.G.A. Championship Will Move from August to May in 2019 |agency=Reuters |date=August 8, 2017 |newspaper=The New York Times |access-date=August 9, 2017 |issn=0362-4331 |archive-date=2021-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210509141437/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/08/08/sports/golf/pga-championship-may.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite magazine |url=https://www.golfdigest.com/story/the-pga-championship-will-be-moving-to-may-sources-say |title=The PGA Championship will be moving to May, sources say |last=Herrington |first=Ryan |magazine=Golf Digest |date=August 7, 2017 |access-date=August 9, 2017 |archive-date=2021-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512151143/https://www.golfdigest.com/story/the-pga-championship-will-be-moving-to-may-sources-say |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

